creator: Buygro
descriptionHtml: The BuyGro Marketplace app is a UAE focused one-stop-shop, with wide inventory visibility and a large market offering that provides thousands of grocery shops, cafes and restaurants with the flexibility and control needed to find new products. It is one of the most advanced apps of its kind in the U.A.E. and promises to deliver value to independent trade buyers as well as distributors. Amongst its benefits, the app closes all distribution gaps, saves time and money, and is easy to use, with zero setup fees involved. In short, it is the perfect tool for a successful trade experience.
